4113354501.Label: Vertex Color Mode: Multi (LE, RE, Op)
4113354501.Description:
This is ignored by this shader package and will be treated as Multi anyway.

Red: Left eye color influence.
Green: Right eye color influence.
Blue: Unused.
Alpha: "Opacity" (only used for the threshold).

3756477356.Label: Color
3756477356.Description: This is ignored by this shader package.

2320401078.Label: Multi (Di, Sp) Map
2320401078.Description:
Red: Diffuse brightness.
Green: Specular strength.

207536625.Label: Normal Map
207536625.Description:

4271961042.Label: Catchlight Map
4271961042.Description:
Red, Green, Blue: Light reflection.
Alpha: Unused.

Sampled at UV that depend on the reflected vector in camera space, regardless of any model UV.
